<p>&nbsp;</p><h2 class="anchor-ready">A Resource for Small Business on the Positive Duty (2023)</h2><span alt="Two workers in a store room working together" data-langcode="en" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="2fa16d87-97a0-4d63-9834-dc0166371f07" data-embed-button="file_browser" data-entity-embed-display="image:image" data-entity-embed-display-settings="{&quot;image_style&quot;:&quot;publication_main_870x500&quot;,&quot;image_link&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;image_loading&quot;:{&quot;attribute&quot;:&quot;lazy&quot;}}" class="embedded-entity">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/publication_main_870x500/public/positive-duty-resources-small-business_0.jpg?itok=Rcu7veaV" width="870" height="500" alt="Two workers in a store room working together" class="image-style-publication-main-870x500">


</span>
<p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Resource for Small Business is designed to promote understanding in the small business community about the new positive duty. This resource includes a brief outline of the positive duty, who it applies to and who it covers. It outlines the steps small businesses can take to satisfy their obligations and provides practical case studies to help small businesses understand the positive duty and take action.</p><h3>Download documents</h3><span data-langcode="en" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="bceaa2be-30db-4429-bca9-48cb8c8370df" data-embed-button="file_browser" data-entity-embed-display="file:file_default" data-entity-embed-display-settings="{&quot;use_description_as_link_text&quot;:1,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Resource for Small Business on The Positive Duty 2023 [PDF]&quot;}" class="embedded-entity"><span class="file file--mime-application-pdf file--application-pdf"><a href="/sites/default/files/2023-08/resource_for_small_business_on_the_positive_duty_2023.pdf" type="application/pdf" title="resource_for_small_business_on_the_positive_duty_2023.pdf">Resource for Small Business on The Positive Duty 2023 [PDF]</a></span>
  <span>(1.53 MB)</span>
</span>
<p>&nbsp;</p><span data-langcode="en" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="f5c82e30-117d-4aad-be87-7e972eac9fbc" data-embed-button="file_browser" data-entity-embed-display="file:file_default" data-entity-embed-display-settings="{&quot;use_description_as_link_text&quot;:1,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Resource for Small Business on the Positive Duty [DOCX]&quot;}" class="embedded-entity"><span class="file file--mime-application-vnd-openxmlformats-officedocument-wordprocessingml-document file--x-office-document"><a href="/sites/default/files/accessible_-_resource_for_small_business_on_the_positive_duty_0.docx" type="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.wordprocessingml.document" title="accessible_-_resource_for_small_business_on_the_positive_duty.docx">Resource for Small Business on the Positive Duty [DOCX]</a></span>
